iv> </div> <div class="pos" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div class="pos-title" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>Co-Founder & CEO,<br data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6><span class="stealth" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6><span class="stealth-bracket" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>&lt;</span>stealth startup<span class="stealth-bracket" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>&gt;</span></span></div> <div class="pos-desc" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>Building next-gen AI-native video infrastructure.</div> </div> </div> <hr class="home-rule" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div class="home-bio" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <p data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6>
